(CONTOSO IT PASSWORD SECURITY POLICY) Tj
0 -20 Td
/F1 11 Tf
(Document: Password Security Policy) Tj
0 -16 Td
(Department: Information Technology) Tj
0 -16 Td
(Classification: Internal | Version: 3.1 | Effective: January 2025) Tj
0 -16 Td
() Tj
0 -16 Td
(1. PURPOSE) Tj
0 -16 Td
(This policy establishes minimum password security standards for all Contoso) Tj
0 -16 Td
(systems to protect against unauthorised access and credential-based attacks.) Tj
0 -16 Td
() Tj
0 -16 Td
(2. PASSWORD REQUIREMENTS) Tj
0 -16 Td
(All user account passwords must meet the following requirements:) Tj
0 -16 Td
(  - Minimum length: 12 characters) Tj
0 -16 Td
(  - Must contain: uppercase letters, lowercase letters, numbers, special characters) Tj
0 -16 Td
(  - Must not contain: username, display name, or common dictionary words) Tj
0 -16 Td
(  - Password history: no reuse for last 12 passwords) Tj
0 -16 Td
() Tj
0 -16 Td
(3. ROTATION POLICY) Tj
0 -16 Td
(Passwords must be changed every 90 days.) Tj
0 -16 Td
(Service account passwords must be changed every 180 days.) Tj
0 -16 Td
(Privileged admin account passwords must be changed every 60 days.) Tj
0 -16 Td
() Tj
0 -16 Td
(4. MULTI-FACTOR AUTHENTICATION) Tj
0 -16 Td
(MFA is REQUIRED for all accounts without exception.) Tj
0 -16 Td
(Approved MFA methods: Microsoft Authenticator app \(preferred\), hardware FIDO2 key.) Tj
0 -16 Td
(SMS-based OTP is not approved for new enrollments.) Tj
0 -16 Td
() Tj
0 -16 Td
(5. PASSWORD STORAGE) Tj
0 -16 Td
(All passwords must be stored in the corporate password manager \(1Password Teams\).) Tj
0 -16 Td
(Passwords must never be stored in plaintext, spreadsheets, or email.) Tj
0 -16 Td
() Tj
0 -16 Td
(6. BREACH RESPONSE PROCEDURE) Tj
0 -16 Td
(If a password is suspected compromised:) Tj
0 -16 Td
(  Step 1: Reset the password immediately via Azure AD self-service portal) Tj
0 -16 Td
(  Step 2: Report the incident to security@contoso.com within 1 hour) Tj
0 -16 Td
(  Step 3: IT Security will review sign-in logs for suspicious activity) Tj
0 -16 Td
(  Step 4: If a data breach is confirmed, follow Incident Response Playbook IR-03) Tj
0 -16 Td
() Tj
0 -16 Td
(Policy owner: IT Security Team | security@contoso.com) Tj
0 -16 Td
